my &mdash; together with its intrinsic credit strengths &mdash; account for Hong Kong's higher rating when compared with China. But the two ratings are clearly interrelated, and the closer the institutional and economic linkages between Hong Kong and China become, the more closely the two ratings will converge.<br />\n<br />\n穆迪都叫你咪痴埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:11:14.000Z","msg":"穆迪同你地講HK=China，大灣區依啲中港fusion <br />\n香港中國評級咪逾近<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c05b16fd5ad96501256902ed6f1e33747cd8383","tid":1574220,"uid":143701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eaa5880d9a8e2a7fdc6336b6ee6aa57b82c243ba","tid":1574220,"uid":125079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd74760c8c21173f0022fee1010fe27c20d4b216","tid":1574220,"uid":143701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6ac3df89b1f479668c9256ebe79c936adf93baf3","tid":1574220,"uid":21398,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:01:34.000Z","msg":"研究緊出緊急法同出解放軍仲係維持評級<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:05:36.000Z","msg":"要降低考慮好多好多野 包括外資本身係香港既利益 但展望負面已經表灑態 你再唔搞好一降就好大獲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:10:09.000Z","msg":"再降<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中共港共一定唔怕， 一定要降咗先逼到佢地<br />\n<br />\n甚至降完都唔撚驚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:11:43.000Z","msg":"無既 中共報署左咁多年既改革開放比林鄭清袋 林鄭仲驚過你"},{"pid":"30494315c89f7f932c69ed673375dccf85adb695","tid":1574220,"uid":224829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:11:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5d97be8726426ec785073c1965c9868d5a2ba7d","tid":1574220,"uid":69916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"063693f822b5317614fc47414cadd4aea0d9be79","tid":1574220,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTi