nk target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n7. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n8. 保持<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span>，分析能力level up，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冷處理fake news/ rumour</span></strong> 、五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n<em>每星期任務：</em><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">低消費</span>，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">做孝子救港</span>，教育家中兩老<br />\n3. 去<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span>貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n<em>每月任務：</em><br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF轉美國<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會、陪審員、派傳單、放映會<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾；Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.16 @Template End@"},{"pid":"b9709d17a1241d9db6b795e78658130d6fdae802","tid":1574220,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:12:32.000Z","msg":"唔降級 屌啦"},{"pid":"4edf6016209a295e43eaee22653b2dcebaa22c60","tid":1574220,"uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:12:52.000Z","msg":"等埋人權法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3866b9d6113f38fc212bf872eb97039f09e0c3ed","tid":1574220,"uid":284429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:16:08.000Z","msg":"香港人齊上齊落<br />\n評級就不上只落"},{"pid":"3d411f7f943148063c4025b3d81e90672db80703","tid":1574220,"uid":263878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:17:25.000Z","msg":"nice, nice,nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d12d1aa966e49d0719f4b073e0c7bac50634393","tid":1574220,"uid":250654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6a919d26bb84a88a644c36dc5a4a0591a46ffd01","tid":1574220,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d0307810b3a9702ff47795d9ab816e5631752381","tid":1574220,"uid":14494,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T10:39:13.000Z","msg":"睇埋佢份報告先<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.moodys.com/research/Moodys-changes-outlook-on-Hong-Kongs-Aa2-rating-to-negative--PR_409149\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moodys.com%2Fresearch%2FMoodys-changes-outlook-on-Hong-Kongs-Aa2-rating-to-negative--PR_409149&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=5e28c59c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.moodys.com/research/Moodys-changes-outlook-on-Hong-Kongs-Aa2-rating-to-negative--PR_409149</a><br />\n<br />\nThe institutional features which grant Hong Kong a degree of political and economic autonomy &mdash; together with its intrinsic credit strengths &mdash; account for Hong Kong's higher rating when compared with China. But the two ratings are clearly interrelated, and the closer the institutional and economic linkages between Hong Kong and China become, the more closely the two ratings will converge.<br />\n<br />\n穆迪都叫你咪痴埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T10:50:43.000Z","msg":"成份報告根本得第一段頭一句講過ongoing protests, 其餘都唔關示威事<br />\n<br />\nMore generally, closer integration between Hong Kong's and China's institutions would point to a narrowing gap between the two ratings. An erosion in China's credit profile would also be negative for Hong Kong's rating."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:17:54.000Z","msg":"只係呢幾個月幫大家睇清D呢個事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"617c388c4843a99729dddc1f1fecb87ba6e44e6a","tid":1574220,"uid":284429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"289ecdebbdfb12ab816a59b31f25a8b95b91e741","tid":1574220,"uid":78392,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T10:44:19.000Z","msg":"次次降級都白紙黑字講明係支那搞香港<br />\n到底點解香港政府可以賴落香港人到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:18:12.000Z","msg":"佢地識字會睇文件？中英聯合聲明都係張廢紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" c